Title: DIZIONARIO Velvet Smooth Foot Care Personal Pedi
Description: Velvet Smooth Foot Care Personal Pedi Foot FilerGentle on your feet and easy to use, the Velvet Smooth Electronic Foot Filer quickly helps you achieve soft, silky feet. This electronic foot file is designed to remove hard skin for smooth results after just one use. It buffs away hard skin in minutes, leaving you with smooth feet you'll want to show off.Velvet Smooth Electronic Pedicure Foot File & Callus Remover Work on 4 AA Batteries (Batteries Not Inclued)How to use:1. Remove the protective roller cover before use.2. Ensure that the roller head is securely inserted into the unit. Do not use without the roller head attached.3. Turn on the unit by twisting the silver ring to the left and gently glide the roller head over hard skin and the dead skin will gradually exfoliate. Use only on dry skin. Do not press too hard, or the unit will stop.4. Turn off and check if you have achieved the softness you desire. If not, turn on and repeat until the level of smoothness is obtained.Warning: Do not use in the same area for more than 3-4 seconds at a time. Stop if skin becomes sore or inflamed.5. Once your feet are starting to resemble smooth, happy feet again, breathe a sign of relief.6. Turn the unit off by twisting the silver ring to the right.7. Wipe or rinse feet to remove excess dead skin particles.8. Thoroughly dry feet.9. Apply moisturiser and massage into your fabulously smooth feet!Warnings:Precautions Keep out of reach of children. For use on hard skin on the feet only. Use only on dry (not wet) skin. Do not use the device anywhere else on the body. Only use for its intended purpose. Do not use in the same area for more than 3-4 seconds at a time. Stop use immediately if irritation or discomfort occurs. Do not use on broken, sore or irritated skin. Do not submerge the device in water. Keep long hair and clothing away from the device when in use. This product is not suitable for diabetics and those with poor blood circulation. We recommend you only use Velvet Smooth Refill Heads with this product.

Moroccan Gossypium Herbaceum fibers tend to negatively charged while human hair tends to be positively charged. Therefore Looks21 Hair Fibers bond to your hair 200% stronger than regular hair building fibers. Natural mineral-based colorants virgin moroccan gossypium herbaceum is grayish white. The fibers are dyed into various colors to match human hair colors. Thanks to the micro-structure of Gossypium Herbaceum its fiber can be easily dyed with mineral-based colorants - iron oxides harvested from nature. Looks21 Hair Fibers is the only 100% natural hair building fiber on the market it is free of synthetic dyes fillers preservatives and animal derivatives. Majik Black Hair Building Fiber (18 grams) With Optimizer Comb(Set of)
Description: Hair loss is a very common problem that number of people suffer from. There are number of products available in the market to prevent this problem. If you are suffering from a drastic hair fall and partial baldness, you could opt for Hair Building Fiber by Majik. Majik is a Swiss based brand which is recognized as one of the most reputed hair-care brands all over the world. From the Manufacturer What It Is Majik Hair Building Fibers, made of 100% Human hair, blend undetectably with existing hair strands to instantly create the appearance of naturally thick and full hair. What It Does Instantly fills in thinning areas Conceals hair loss Makes fine hair look completely thick and full Great as a root touch-up between colorings What Else You Need To Know Majik Hair Fibers resist wind, rain, and perspiration for long lasting results in all conditions. Available in nine shades that can be mixed to match Indian hair color, Hair Fibers work for all hair types and textures. Also great for part lines, covering extension tracks and touching up roots between hair color appointments. Easily washes out with shampoo. How to Apply Dry and style hair as usual. Shake Hair Fibers into thinning areas. If applying Hair Fibers near the hairline, use Majik Hairline Optimizer to achieve a natural looking front hairline. Gently pat hair to disperse Hair Fibers. If desired, lightly comb, brush, or style your hair after applying Hair Fibers. For best results, use Majik Hair Fiber Spray to finish for longer-lasting results.
